{"tid":754425,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"專家：遇強風靠「大耳朵」急降","createTime":"2018-07-24T11:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T13:11:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6813100ce3d17557a4419d9bbfb66b7c856a1692","tid":754425,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:44:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180724/20458677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180724%2F20458677&d=UIUFL9x5%2FU%2FE5XejIp7dPzANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=c9a2d774\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180724%2F20458677&h=378359e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180724/20458677</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月24日 <br />\n<br />\n專家：遇強風靠「大耳朵」急降<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180724/large/a0502a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180724%2Flarge%2Fa0502a.gif&h=0ca4d446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■事主失蹤前使用同一個藍、黃及紫色滑翔傘。香港滑翔傘聯會提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港約有逾300人活躍玩滑翔傘，香港滑翔傘協會安全主任趙浩南指，類似前日突然出現強陣風的情況過去很少，運動員若遇緊急情況，一般會做俗稱「大耳朵」動作協助降落。<br />\n<br />\n趙稱，滑翔傘玩者若遇天氣轉壞，會即時緊急降落，做一個稱為「大耳朵」及加速的動作，即拉動其中兩條傘繩，令主傘兩端翼尖的面積對稱地收細，從而快速下降。「今次（強陣風）嚟得太快，想降已經嚟到」。他續稱，一般滑翔傘飛行員都應隨身攜帶自身衞星定位、無線電對講機、手機等，有部份衞星定位有實時追蹤功能。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n飛行前須有牌<br />\n<br />\n另外，滑翔傘基本裝備包括主傘、座袋、副傘（救生傘）。全港可玩滑翔傘地點有8個，包括浪茄灣、北潭坳、八仙嶺、馬鞍山、西灣、石澳、南大嶼山郊野公園西部及東部，有固定範圍及高度限制。<br />\n<br />\n本港有不同機構提供滑翔傘課程，一般分五級，趙稱巿民如想獨自玩，須跟隨認可的教練上堂及實習，並通過國際航空聯盟認可的三級課程考試，經批核獲取相關牌照才可在本港飛行。<br />\n<br />\n修讀第一至三級滑翔傘課程，所需學費至少兩萬元，而買基本裝備約花費4萬元。第四級課程即失蹤者鍾旭華已通過的考試屬進階級，第五級屬高級飛行員課程。目前當局並無官方滑翔傘發牌機制，只是依賴體育總會管理。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張珮琪  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n最後訊號來自芝麻灣　 海陸空尋滑翔男　 搜救30小時<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n事發時風速飆至60km/h<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事發時風速飆至60km/h<br />\n<br />\n「山神」折返　天文台掛一號波<br />\n<br />\n最後訊號來自芝麻灣　海陸空尋滑翔男　搜救30小時"},{"pid":"a475e4dda00b4ab6ba45ba07f7cd8464013eff9c","tid":754425,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:58:26.000Z","msg":"玩過GTA當自己專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4820cd2295975723b080cbc3edd5282b919a7d65","tid":754425,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a475e4dda00b4ab6ba45ba07f7cd8464013eff9c","tid":754425,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:58:26.000Z","msg":"玩過GTA當自己專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508fdf96b0c12395e9056ef2c00b2dbd6f40f983","tid":754425,"uid":177047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4820cd2295975723b080cbc3edd5282b919a7d65","tid":754425,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a475e4dda00b4ab6ba45ba07f7cd8464013eff9c","tid":754425,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:58:26.000Z","msg":"玩過GTA當自己專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:07:46.000Z","msg":"玩過gta5,跳傘槍戰夜襲甩身都係小兒科<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ada53fd9d4f4ab38deb8b87c336b33a51c18da","tid":754425,"uid":165213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:26:02.000Z","msg":"有污糟野"},{"pid":"7b3d4f9cf28a7ee8b8e526724de277cc16a049ba","tid":754425,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:30:57.000Z","msg":"衝上雲霄"},{"pid":"d0c768f74d1f0c6d9a69a84257d25adb82b3ee0d","tid":754425